title: Fictional Women Around the World: Terra Branford
itunes:title: Fictional Women Around the World: Terra Branford
description:
We're taking it down nostalgia lane with the Super Nintendo hero Terra Branford from Final Fantasy 3/6, depending on your version. Part human, part ethereal creature, all pixelated glory, Terra's journey of self-discovery is one that still resonates.
